---
functions:
  file-read:
  - binary: false
    code: |-
      tac -s 'RANDOM' /path/to/input-file
    comment: |-
      Make sure that `RANDOM` does not appear into the file to read otherwise the content of the file is corrupted by reversing the order of `RANDOM`-separated chunks.
    contexts:
      sudo:
      suid:
      unprivileged:
...
